{"data":[{"id":562970340,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562970340","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546167558,"updated_time":1546167568,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"comment_count":13,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e有幸看到这位陈同学的证明，激动万分。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到他在邮件中填写的个人信息和他的个人说明。他是一个高三的学生，学的是理科，他也说了他为什么想去证明哥德巴赫猜想，他只不过是想保送清华和北大。因为他偏科太严重，数学物理每次考试接近满分，而英语在30分上下徘徊。而他又非常想进清华北大，迫不得已，他才去证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他说他在一个偶然的机会，他看到一位同学刘路，中南大学数学系学生，大三时独立解决了西塔潘猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e于是，他想通过证明哥德巴赫猜想的方式保送清华北大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  看完他的证明，用的是基本的初中数学函数知识和高中的几何知识。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  证明方法很简单，但是，有几个关键步骤我不是很理解，一些化简使用的数学公式难以看懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  以前在数学的学习中没有看到过这类公式，我尝试去推理，但也没有推理出来。我感觉这些数学公式哪个地方有问题，但又说不明白，希望各位同道中人指点迷津。作为数学系的副教授，无颜面对各位数学同行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  还请各位敬待佳音，元旦他会把证明过程在知乎发布，到那时，大家可以一饱眼福了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，向这位同学致敬，他身为高三学生，在学业繁忙之际，为了保送清华北大。而不畏艰辛困难去证明哥德巴赫猜想，非常值得表扬。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  希望这位陈同学能够继续保持对数学的热情，让中国的数学事业成为世界的典范。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  谢谢你的来信，祝前程似锦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e                  ——2018年12月30日于北京\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"有幸看到这位陈同学的证明，激动万分。看到他在邮件中填写的个人信息和他的个人说明。他是一个高三的学生，学的是理科，他也说了他为什么想去证明哥德巴赫猜想，他只不过是想保送清华和北大。因为他偏科太严重，数学物理每次考试接近满分，而英语在30分上下…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1348\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Ce